title: [The Greater of Two Weevils]
description: An assortment of mats is scattered over the tent floor, each made of bamboo slats painted with red poppies and sepia leaves.  Colorful paper lanterns strung overhead illuminate a series of wooden display racks poised atop a raised platform.  An unopened crate branded with strange markings has been pushed out of the way and partially concealed by a large earthenware pot.
